textBeforeTable: 2011-12 Women's Basketball Roster Before FHU: Prepped at Red Boiling Springs HS where she put together one of the best careers in school history scoring 2,534 career pointsmade 342 career 3-pointers including 111 as a seniora three-time all-state selection, she became the school's all-time leading scorer and 3-point shooter during her junior seasonshot 82.7 percent from the free throw line during her career and totaled 323 assists and 221 stealsas a senior, averaged 19.8 points per game while shooting 35 percent from 3-point range and 87.3 percent from the charity stripewas a two-time District 8A MVP and was named to the Region 4A All-Region team as a junior and senior. --> {page:Section1;} div.Section1 mso-paper-source:0;} mso-footer-margin:.5in; mso-header-margin:.5in; margin:1.0in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in; {size:8.5in 11.0in; @page Section1 mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman";} mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"; font-family:"Times New Roman"; font-size:12.0pt; mso-pagination:widow-orphan; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin:0in; mso-style-parent:""; {mso-style-name:Style-1; p.Style-1, li.Style-1, div.Style-1 mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman";} mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"; font-family:"Times New Roman"; font-size:12.0pt; mso-pagination:widow-orphan; margin-bottom:.0001pt; margin:0in; {mso-style-parent:""; p., li., div. /* Style Definitions */
